해 준다고 보면 된다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The keyof operator takes an object type and produces a string or numeric literal union of its keys.</p>\n<p><small class=\"caption\"><a href=\"https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/handbook/2/keyof-types.html\">— Typescript Documentation</a></small></p>\n</blockquote>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container abyss grvsc-ps-tiaGIi grvsc-ps-tlfloc\" data-language=\"ts\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-tiaGIi-13 grvsc-tiaGIi-b grvsc-tlfloc-4\">type</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-5 grvsc-t9ljLd-u grvsc-tiaGIi-7 grvsc-tlfloc-10\">Coordinate</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-7 grvsc-tiaGIi-8 grvsc-tlfloc-1\">=</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> { </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-12\">lon</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-7 grvsc-tiaGIi-8 grvsc-tlfloc-1\">:</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-tiaGIi-8 grvsc-tlfloc-10\">number</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\">; </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-12\">lan</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-7 grvsc-tiaGIi-8 grvsc-tlfloc-1\">:</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> </span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-tiaGIi-8 grvsc-tlfloc-10\">number</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi-1 grvsc-tlfloc-1\"> }</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-15 grvsc-t9ljLd-i grvsc-tiaGIi-13 grvsc-tiaGIi-b grvsc-tlfloc-4\">type</span><span class=\"grvsc-t9ljLd-1 grvsc-tiaGIi